      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kanaäna Semmi iſluhko/ ko eſ̄ teem Israëta Behrneem dohmu/ no ikweenas Zilts buhs tew weenâ Wihrnu tuhtiht / kas wiſſi Wirfneeki irr winnu Starpâ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad iſfuhtija Mohsus tohs no Pahrana Tuḱneses / pehz ta KU NGA Wahrdn / wiſſi tee Wihrı bija Wirfneeki to Israëta Behrnu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ſchee irr winnu Wahrdı / no Ruhbera Zilts / Sammuifs/ Zakura Dehls.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "No Sihmeana Zilts/ Sabwats / Korus Dehls.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "No Juhda Zilts/ Kahlebs/ Jeiwuna Dehls.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "No Ihsakara Zilts/ Ji-geals/ Jahsepa Dehls.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "No Eewraima Zilts/ Ose-us/ Nuuna Dehls.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "No Benjaminia Zilts / Paltus / Rapus Dehls.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "No Sebulana Zilts/ Gad-diels/ Sohdus Dehls.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "No Jahsepa Zilts/ preekſch Manaffus Zilti/ Gaddus/ Suh-fus Dehls.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "No Danna Zilts / Am-miets/ Gemallus Dehls.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "No Ahsera Zilts/ Seturs/ Mikkata Dehls.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "No Nawtata Zilts / Nakbus/ Wawsus Dehls.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "No Gada Zilts / Guëls/ Mahkus Dehls.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Schee irr to Wihrnu Wahrdı/ ko Mohsus to Semmi iſluh-kohı fuhtija/ un Mohsus noẜauze Oseü/ Nuuna Dehın Josuüs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Mohsus fuhtija tohs/ to Kanaäna Semmi iſluhkoht / un fazziin us teem : Zelleetees Scheit prett Deenas-Widdu / un eite augſcham us teem Kalneem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un apraugajt to Semini/ kahda ta irr / un tohs Laidis/ kaß eekſch tahs dsihwo / arrig tee stipri jeb wahji/ masjeb dauds irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un kahda ta Semme irr/ kur eekſcha tee dsihwo / arrig ta labba jeb tanna/un kahdi Pilsfah-ti tur irr/ kur eekſcha tee dsihwo/ arrig tee Lehgerös jeb stipraß Pil-lis dsihwo.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Arridsan kahda ta Sem-me irr / arrig tauka jeb leefa/ arrig Kohki eekſch tahs jeb ne. Ef-feet drohſchi/ un xemmeetees lihds no teem Semmes Augteem; jo tas notikke paſcha pirnajo Wiyna-Ohgı Laika.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee aisgahje un iſluh-koja to Semmi/ no tahs Tuḱ-nefes Zin / lihds Rekobun / fur eets tohp us Amatu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee aisgahje prett Dee-nas-Widdu / un nahze Eebronâ/ un tur bija Akinaüs / Sesäüs / un Talinaüs / Eenaka Behrni. Bet Eebrons bija ſeptix Gaddus preekſch Zoana/ Egiptes-Semmê uhszelts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un pehz nahze tee pee to Eskoleſtippi / un nogreese no tur-renes weenu Stihgu ar weenu Sarri / pilnu ar Wihrnu-Kekka-reem/ to paſchu nefſe diwi us wee- nu neffann Rahrti/ ir no Grana-ta-Ahbofeem / un no Wihrgehim.\n"
    }
  ],
